What is user agent: User agent is a special string header, which enables the server to identify the operating system and version, CPU type, browser and version, browser rendering engine, browser language, browser plug-in, etc.
What is mixed content mode: Specifies the mixed content mode. i.e WebView will allow a secure origin to load content from any other origin.
What is mixed content mode_Never: Never - WebView will not allow a secure origin to load content from an insecure origin.
What is mixed content mode_Always: Always - WebView will allow a secure origin to load content from any other origin, even if that origin is insecure.
What is mixed content mode_Compatibility: Compatibility - WebView will attempt to be compatible with the approach of a modern web browser with regard to mixed content.
